content: I think I'll focus on updating my coffee table first. I've actually been looking for a new one, and I found a great deal on a mid-century modern-style coffee table on Craigslist. Speaking of furniture, I just assembled a 5-shelf bookcase from IKEA last weekend, and it was a great deal - only $80 for such a big and sturdy bookcase!
